{"tid":42783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女酒後亂性懷孕結婚　老公才知兒子是小王的","createTime":"2016-12-17T03:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T10:17:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"421607e853c9af17babe148f1f4b5a02bb2a0b53","tid":42783,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:58:45.000Z","msg":"中國一名林姓女子和吳姓男子在2015年奉子成婚，生下一名兒子，但經過親子鑑定，吳男才發現兒子不是他的。之後林女承認，因為一次的酒後亂性，懷上了「小王」張姓男子的種，兩人也因而離婚。 <br />\n<br />\n據中國《網易》報導，林女與吳男交往已久，但也同時和張男有來往，某晚林女和張男約會，喝了點酒後就上床，之後林女就懷孕了。吳男以為林女懷了他的孩子，兩人在2015年奉子成婚。由於婚後僅3個月，兒子就早產出生，派出所以林女懷孕3個月後結婚為由，要求進行親子鑑定。本以為只是例行的手續，沒想到鑑定結果出來，讓所有人都驚呆了！孩子竟然不是吳男的種。這時林女才全盤說出與張男酒後亂性的事，最後兩人也以離婚收場。 <br />\n<br />\n事後林女要求張男認子，但張男一直逃避，拒絕進行親子鑑定。之後林女撿了一個張男丟在法院的水瓶送檢，也確立了張男與孩子的親子關係。最後法院判決孩子跟著林女生活，而張男每月支付撫養費2000元人民幣(約新台幣1萬元)，直至其18歲。 <br />\n<br />\n（施旖婕／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"3d8954c4e19b6c583567538f69e8bd0d6aac4b47","tid":42783,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"點解我會看左小王是兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f38f8d7d75e7d9306af56a9ca815f9a1df180c","tid":42783,"uid":2259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31bda888be701ce321c6bf1cf4320a18ad6726d","tid":42783,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"合符國情"},{"pid":"517d5a05fab4c12e8a38bf4d60fa4a47f6461a5d","tid":42783,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"無結婚+唔認數都要俾分手費？"},{"pid":"c5f27f524931a06a58aa6e0b8ab109ed5e77e3eb","tid":42783,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"珀琥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f50cd63e4faebc80982bb53c4943860225aa4c","tid":42783,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解我會看左小王是兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為係隻狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ce787f3e78ed12ec5ef5552d47a80324c5a3db","tid":42783,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"冇結婚都要俾撫養費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea5d7d1bb929a631b857ee358905c96a46efece","tid":42783,"uid":6208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"（施旖婕／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"3eebb78c8ace84f691fdf0eeebc9733f2bbf9141","tid":42783,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"酒後亂性都信"},{"pid":"655f568c85ec3e4c2fb06f98be0f664ca454a903","tid":42783,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d2fb8c77e08899cca8d763745b8a5f0ea3c7bac","tid":42783,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}